<article id="home">
<div class="jumbotron">
   
<div class="well">
   
  
<h1><span class="fa fa-step-forward"></span> MovieQueue</h1>
<h2>Track the movies you've seen, list and tag the ones you plan to watch, and share lists with friends.</h2>

<% if current_user.present? %>
<h2>USER IS LOGGED IN</h2>
  <p>As a MovieQueue user, you started with an initial <%= link_to "list", user_lists_path(current_user), id: "list_index_link_homepage" %>. You can browse movies and add them to your list.</p>
  <p>You can create as many lists as you'd like (all-time faves, 80s action movies, movies starring William H. Macy...whatever you'd like).</p>
  <p>You can also check out what <%= link_to "lists other users", public_lists_path, id: "public_lists_link_homepage" %> have created.</p>
  <p><%= link_to "Search by movie title", api_search_path, id: "movie_title_search_link_homepage" %> </p>
  <p><%= link_to "Search by actor", actor_search_path, id: "actor_search_link_homepage" %> </p>
  <p><%= link_to "Search by all sorts of things", discover_search_path, id: "discover_search_link_homepage" %> </p>
<% else %>
<div class="button-holder">
   

  <p class="button-large"><%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, id: "sign_in_nav_link" %></p>
  <p class="button-main"><%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, id: "sign_up_nav_link" %></p>
</div> <!-- button holder -->


<% end %><!-- current_user? -->

</div> <!-- well -->

</div> <!-- jumbotron -->

</article>



